Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.39,0:01:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三话\N悲伤的剑士\N斩断过去的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.37,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷道场踏出再建的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.61,0:01:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄食的剑客 剑心加入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个弟子是明神祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.65,0:01:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么训练的第三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也先从深呼吸开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.79,0:02:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛闭起来。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷活心流的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.87,0:02:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么活心流嘛我已经厌烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.61,0:02:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候\N你才会教我对抗敌人的方法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这想法就不对了！\N我不是说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.78,0:02:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活心流是保护人的剑法了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护人？哇啊。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.65,0:02:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！我是为了要\N成为强者才到这里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要保护人的剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而希望你教我打倒敌人的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.69,0:02:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小生的剑法没有打算留在后世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦的师父是小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等！等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！剑心这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫人家要成为强者的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这么坏的小孩子推给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃自己做的不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.57,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剑心做的比较好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的你的好胜心\N虽然可怕的有点象我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是感觉象是\N拥有成绩不好的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.35,0:03:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我也是觉得你很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是看到那剑心之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是。。真不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么厉害的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么待在这\N名不经传的小道馆呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂阿熏剑心到道是何人物呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是。。什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那对敌的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象杀了很多人的感觉。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！！\N那家伙真正的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是以前的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山贼吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在一定被警察追捕着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太帅了！！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是。。。\N为什么会成为流浪人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是完成明治维新的志士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末年的动乱之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心为什么会消失呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个谜。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谣传说杀了不该杀的人。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道太多的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被明治政府追杀着。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是。。！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是小熏小姐的午餐！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快还给我！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个笨蛋！！\N为什么要有秘密呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害人家这么担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把真的事情说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行。。\N不可以问别人的过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.25,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那。。那个\N问你这种事也许不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是一点点就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什么事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.36,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去买豆腐了今天要吃好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.17,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连我的份也要帮我煮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是。是吗。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么你们这些家伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这道场的负责人叫来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要麻烦人之前\N首先要自报姓名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你。你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我，我是神谷熏师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗不是很无礼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看那样子连三岁小孩也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,署长！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心。。\N拔刀斋应该是在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋？是指杀人拔刀斋吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剑心吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.41,0:06:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假拔刀斋被捕的人证实了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在这道场里。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果隐藏了国家罪犯是犯罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.52,0:07:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心你说剑心做了什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是等在外面的人\N才知道政府机密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来搜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟拔刀斋一起你想死刑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去通知剑心\N回来会被捕的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿。。阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要了。。总算让我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.39,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要。。见面了\N绯村。。拔刀斋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雀也。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.87,0:07:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太急否则豆腐会破掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看有带刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙真是大胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的就违抗废刀令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.35,0:08:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者你想在\N剑客警官的面前一决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜了我就让你逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有小孩子在。。。\N求求你不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逆刃刀？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈。。那东西\N连一只老鼠都不能杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窝囊废！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.47,0:08:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.15,0:08:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是坏人，把我们豆腐弄倒了\N不道歉是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开！鬼叫的小孩给我让开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑客警官大人要通过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑客警官队。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小偷你死了这条心吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧\N这是我偶发起的歹意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们饶了他吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.95,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只被拿走一条擦手巾而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.32,0:09:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻烦各位剑客警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我们在就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些乡下的三等巡查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.36,0:09:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要对我们抗议吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我们是萨摩的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不我。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说些什么。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是剑客警官队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被挑选出来的精选部队。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们这些无名小卒不一样\N被允许带刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之杀人是被政府所准许的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，拔刀吧。。\N会把你杀了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心剑心！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心你在哪里呢？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我父亲也捉走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他坦护犯罪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要在这里碍手碍脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有哪一位有哪一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请救救我父亲！他是无罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他女儿也捉起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些人真是乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当作教训把他们全部处死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑客好象变迟钝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔不杀人是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！！放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说要处死刑。。。？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没有犯什么罪。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了这村里的治安！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.21,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好的芽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.31,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不从小的时候连根拔起的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这关系着犯罪的防止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好的是你们！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口！！你也会被杀的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？刚刚的精神呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.90,0:11:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住。。住手！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你。你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样！！等一下！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！！剑心快逃。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人要来捉你。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.86,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁。。？报上名来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.04,0:12:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被绑在这里的每个人\N如果真的有罪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小生愿意代替他们受罪。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之你是不服气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这东京府下带刀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定对于\N自己的剑法有相当的自信。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.22,0:12:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙只是胆小鬼而己！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定。。。？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这男人。。有血的味道。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了我找到了！！\N红色头发！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸颊上有十字的伤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象绯村的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在跟剑客警官队为敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.02,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下捉起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思有一点痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会把剑心交给你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等。。。等一下。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了拔刀吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个一个。。。的处死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.71,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是横行暴道\N已经看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是警官就可以这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敢骂剑客警察队的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有胆量。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用抗拒官吏罪！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部给我逮捕起来！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.73,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,允许拔剑！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.03,0:14:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗的人没关系给我杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.45,0:14:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰那些没有罪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.69,0:14:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要找对手的话找小生就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要舔地面的人尽管过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是。。正当防卫成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他。。。！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下。。。一个人。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.43,0:15:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟这村里的人发誓\N不要再模行暴道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你要以违反废刀令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.37,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或伤害罪将小生逮捕也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑！！\N说得跟真的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开！！让开！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快让开！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊这是？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.66,0:15:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男人是绯村拔刀斋！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那架式是。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨摩的最强的剑法\N二太刀示现流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是示现流\N是非常豪爽的剑法。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.88,0:15:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在飞天御剑流前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是完全。。。发挥不了作用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害真是不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.14,0:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人也没有杀死就能摆平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英雄。。！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是久留的地方！！\N快逃。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.68,0:16:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察是来捉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是国家追捕的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连剑客警官也。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉起来！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到民众的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.41,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就知道谁是对的！放开他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于这些人的横行暴道行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好的给我处罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村。。总算见到你了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这十年里。。我一直找你。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.66,0:17:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在流行留胡子吗。。山县先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危陷的！！还不知道这位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不知道吗！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村曾经用那把剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.30,0:17:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救过很多维新志士的命的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,态度给我谨慎一点！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山县。。。！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是山县。。有朋！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？总之他是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很伟大的老先生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.52,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗\N明治政府陆军队的山县有朋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在日本顶点的政治家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边有马车在等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情想要跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,。。在这里不行吗。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真象是你的作风。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村。。没有你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维新是没办法成立的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为创造这国家的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你加入\N帝国陆军成为干部。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.49,0:18:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维新的同志\N大家都希望你能回去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.79,0:18:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何\N请支持帮助明治政府！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的对不起。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想以杀人的功劳\N而担任政府的要职。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是。。。你会消失。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是表示你不想再杀人的决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.56,0:18:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是杀人那也是\N维新大业中重要的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不承认这点之辈\N我也不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用权力去压倒别人！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.83,0:19:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,。。。这种想法。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.47,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才会有这种傲慢的男人。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.28,0:19:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经用剑去奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了权力和光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.78,0:19:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了创造\N让人们能幸福生活的社会。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.79,0:19:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些都忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是暴发户而已吧。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.43,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是绯村！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时代已经改变了\N现在是明治时代！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.37,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实行废刀令。武士已经消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有权力了在这明治的社会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭一把剑什么也不能做的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有一把剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能用这只眼睛阻止的话。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能保护什么吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃的。。绯村。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有一把剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能用这只眼睛阻止的话。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能保护什么吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护人的剑。。。。吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？祢彦。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.87,0:20:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始你要记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.87,0:20:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是杀人的剑。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是保护人的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为强者。。用活心流。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了。。保护人。。。？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.66,0:21:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好做阿熏的弟子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛这时候还。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.90,0:21:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从一开始就是我的弟子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我当成小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是小孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.84,0:21:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心为什么成为流浪汉。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.81,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于有点明白了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想被任何事拘束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想过自由自在的生活。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.78,0:21:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那剑是为了能\N自由自在的保护人们。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们的剑心
